  "response": "To add a profile picture on Quora, follow these steps:\n\n1. Log in to your Quora account\n\n2. Click on your profile icon in the top right corner of the screen\n\n3. Select \"Settings\" from the dropdown menu\n\n4. Under the \"Profile\" section, click on your current profile picture\n\n5. Choose \"Upload a photo\" or drag and drop an image file\n\n6. Crop the image as desired\n\n7. Click \"Save\" to set your new profile picture\n\nMake sure the image is high-quality and meets Quora's upload requirements (typically under a certain file size and in common image formats like JPG or PNG).",
